Program: Omnibus
Title: Nkrumah - the Cancer of Betrayal
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376m1r
Last Broadcast Date: 06 September 2000
'Forward ever, backward never'. Exploring the life and times of the first president of Ghana, Kwame Nkrumah, and the coup that overthrew him. Contributors include his son Kamal Nkrumah.